SummaryEnglish: Thirteen years ago, the Villainous Army of evil attempted to invade Earth, faced by the super sentai squadron known as the Dragon Keepers, and their super weapons, the Divine Tools. The evil army, however, was defeated within a year, all of its executives wiped out, and the surviving (and almost immortal) foot soldiers have been forced ever since to reenact their defeat to the Keepers in front of a crowd of spectators every Sunday. Tired of the charade, and realizing that this amounts to little more than slavery, one of the foot soldiers rebels, and decides he will defeat the Dragon Keepers by infiltrating the organization.

1.TitleEnglish: We Are Justice! The Dragon Keepers!
1.SummaryEnglish: Tired of the Sunday Showdown charade, Fighter D decides to defeat the Rangers for real this time.

2.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D reunites with Yumeko Suzukiri, who approaches him with an unexpected proposal.

3.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D decides to infiltrate the Red Garrison with Yumeko, only to find himself in a tight spot.

4.SummaryEnglish: In pursuit of Fighter D, Aran Hekiru, a Blue Junior Third Rank, discovers his connection to Hibiki.

5.TitleEnglish: Fighter D, as a Part of "Ranger Force"
5.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D infiltrates the White Dragon's Nest in disguise and discovers someone in hiding.

6.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D and Kai Shion work together to face off against Shun Tokita in the final exam.

7.TitleEnglish: The Zigzag Road to the Final Exam!
7.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D's plans go awry as Shion works with the other cadets on the second day of the exam.

8.SummaryEnglish: Peltrola sneaks into the White Dragon's Nest, and meets Komachi Aizome of the Blue Squadron.

9.SummaryEnglish: Fighter XX steps in to help Fighter D but is stopped by Blue Keeper with his Divine Artifact.

10.SummaryEnglish: Peltrola retreats after an all-out fight with Blue Keeper, but is halted by the Junior First Ranks.

11.TitleEnglish: On the Road to My Justice!
11.SummaryEnglish: The cadets, Junior First Ranks, and Blue Keeper team up against Peltrola and their clones.

12.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D engages in a head-to-head fight with Blue Keeper despite his overwhelming disadvantage.

1.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D encounters Chidori, a peculiar man investigating a string of mysterious disappearances.

2.TitleEnglish: For This School, in This Moment
2.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D and his squadmates encounter an enigmatic organization and are trapped in an illusion.

3.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D and Hisui prepare for combat as the Green Squadron reunites with someone unexpected.

4.TitleEnglish: Make Our Dreams Come True, Ranger Force
4.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D turns the tide of the battle searching for a way back into the illusory school.

5.TitleEnglish: The Arrival of Green  ~The Maji Tsuyo Force~
5.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D continues his search for the boss monster Magatia with Hisui and Nishiki, a detective.

6.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D begins executing his plan to take down the Green Keeper with Suzukiri's help.

7.TitleEnglish: We Are the Monster Protection Society
7.SummaryEnglish: While the Ranger Force's deception is revealed, a new organization begins to lurk behind the scenes.

8.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D and Hisui confront Yakushi Usukubo, the Head Director of the Monster Protection Society.

9.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D learns the shocking truth behind the Divine Artifacts, Dragon Keepers, and monsters.

10.SummaryEnglish: The thread of fate connecting Hibiki and Sesera begins unraveling towards an unexpected outcome.

11.SummaryEnglish: As the world is under attack by the Monster Army, Fighter D renews his resolve once again.

12.TitleEnglish: The One and Only Fighter D
12.SummaryEnglish: Fighter D decides to cooperate with the Ranger Force temporarily to corner Deathmecia.
